  "summary": "Space Exploration Technologies Corp., doing business as SpaceX, is an American spaceflight, telecommunications, and artificial intelligence company headquartered at the Starbase development site in Starbase, Texas. The company operates 3 divisions: \"Space\", which conducts more orbital launches annually than any other launch provider, including national programs; \"Connectivity\", which operates Starlink, a communications satellite company; and \"Artificial intelligence\", which operates Grok, X, and data centers.",
